                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have been playing with my mage off and on, so far up to lvl 26.
<br />
My current tactics are frostbolt, fireball, fireblast, ball, blast.. until critter is dead..
<br />
It is a little rough on health and mana, and if I get a resist or two, things go downhill quickly.
<br />
With the druid, I haven't grouped with any mages, so I haven't had a chance to ask about their tactics, although I have discovered in a group, mage tactics greatly differ.
<br />
Any suggestions from you magi out there?</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=247107" target="_blank" class="postlink">Goloth</a>
<br />
