                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">That's close to what I do when soloing with my mage (level 30). But I put enough talent points into arcane to make my arcane missiles uninterruptible. That makes a tremendous difference when a mob gets into melee range. Non-elites usually only get one or two hits in. Routine is frostbolt, fireball, fireblast, arcane missiles, and if needed alternate fireblast and arcane missiles from then on.
<br />

<br />
Instant-cast arcane explosion also makes me very popular in Gnomeregan. Now that I've got it it's back to fire though. I'll probably respec to frost later, but word is frost isn't much use unless you have a lot of talent points to put into it.
<br />

<br />
Teremar Talfirien</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
